data.description: beautiful and well kept 4 bedroom home located right in Moncks Corner. This home is on a HUGE quarter of an acre lot. Spacious Formal dining room and Living room boasts a really incredible fireplace. The kitchen has more than enough counter space for all of your needs. The master bedroom upstairs has a walk in closet, tray ceiling and upgraded bathrooms. You also have 3 other bedrooms that are a great size. This house is move in ready! Come park in your two car garage.
